reviewText:
These people with "unauthorized" really need to get their sh@!% strait! As an island born and follower of Reaggaeton and it's strongest representative, this documentary lacks professionalism. It's basically video shots that have nothing to do with what is being narrated. I've seen similar reviews for people who bought other artist bio's through this production co.
Like I said The King deserves better! As a matter of fact if I was his representative or part of management, I would have made sure they did a better job
